data.description: Masthope Contemporary style home situated on 1.08 Acre FLAT lot. Great location in community offering privacy and plenty of room to expand or build your dream a garage. Home offers 3BD/2BA/open floor plan, unfinished basement w/ rough plumbing, screened in porch, LP fireplace and spacious loft. Home is being sold turnkey and move in ready. Masthope amenities offer skiing, lodge/bar/restaurant, pickleball/basketball/tennis courts, motor boating lake w/ beach, 2 outdoor pools, tiki bar, ATV trails, fitness center, horseback riding, Delaware River park/river access, minigolf and many weekly activities for the whole family.
